original: Jerndal, Gösta, tandläkare, Göteborg, f. 4/6/04 i Gbg av disp. Harald August J. o. Sigrid Mathilda Artelius. G. 33 m. Sonja Armstedt. Barn: Lars f. 34, Ulf 37, Ann 39. — Stud:ex. v. Gbgs h. real 23, Cand. med. dent. i Berlin 29, tysk tandl. i Leipzig 31, sv. dito 32. Prakt, i Gbg o. Kungälv sed. 32. Jerneryd’, Oiscar Folke Roland, civilingenjör, förste baningenjör, Borås, f. 27/5/15 i Gbg. G. 41 m. Anna-Stina Ekström. Barn: Lena f. 42, Björn 44. — Stud:ex. i Gbg 35, civ:-ing:ex. v. CTH (VoV) 40. An.st. v. Hugo L Andreassons ing:byrå i Gbg 40-41, h. SJ fr. 41, v. banavd. Örebro 41-42, Borås 43-44, Nässjö 45-46, Borås 47, förste baning. där. Hobby: sport, konst.
translated: Jerndal, Gösta, dentist, Gothenburg, b. 4/6/04 in Gothenburg to Harald August J. and Sigrid Mathilda Artelius. Married in 1933 to Sonja Armstedt. Children: Lars b. 1934, Ulf b. 1937, Ann b. 1939. Education: secondary school diploma from Gothenburg high school (real program) in 1923, dental degree in Berlin in 1929, German dental degree in Leipzig in 1931, Swedish dental degree in 1932. Practice in Gothenburg and Kungälv since 1932. Jerneryd', Oscar Folke Roland, civil engineer, chief railway engineer, Borås, b. 27/5/15 in Gothenburg. Married in 1941 to Anna-Stina Ekström. Children: Lena b. 1942, Björn b. 1944. Education: secondary school diploma in Gothenburg in 1935, civil engineering degree from Chalmers University of Technology in 1940. Worked for Hugo L Andreasson's engineering firm in Gothenburg from 1940-41, Swedish State Railways from 1941, railway department in Örebro from 1941-42, Borås from 1943-44, Nässjö from 1945-46, Borås in 1947, and became the chief railway engineer there. Hobbies: sports, art.
